title: ‘My’ Discord Channel
body:
Some people were led to join “my” FitGirl channel on Discord. Like before with “my” Twitter, Facebook, YouTube, you name it.

One more time – I didn’t, don’t and will not have any pages but this site. Everything else is fake. You can get malware and other shit in there. But if you’re a dumb fucker, please join those – I don’t care. Dumb fuckers must suffer.
